{"tid":2193138,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日本的味道: 梅干 （梅干し）","createTime":"2020-09-07T14:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T11:23:19.000Z","uid":194483,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c98eec73e7ff653eda578ec4dc5667fbfedb4e","tid":2193138,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇自家浸梅酒呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每年6月就係青梅0既季節<br />\n我最早有一樽2011年仲係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知大家知唔知今年日本青梅失收 (好似因為天氣/武肺等等)<br />\n黎到香港D貨都<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我提早半年訂左一箱紀州南高梅 黎到香港店家話熟晒出唔到貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁6月中終於忍唔住, 見街市生果檔都有賣完熟梅, 唔整梅酒就試下整梅干啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(其實之後都整左梅酒0既, 有興趣可以另一個PO分享)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TT6ApNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTT6ApNY.jpg&h=e4884d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紀州, 即古時和歌山, 出產青梅係日本最出名<br />\n買左D完熟南高梅, 應該SIZE有2~3L (我訂果箱係4L... 可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n好黃, 帶D紅, 完熟梅淋身同有桃0既香味<br />\n買返黎洗乾淨, 去椗, 抹乾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGZKibO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGZKibO.jpg&h=c3f662eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n消毒個樽, 一定要好乾淨, 否則會發霉, 咁就GG<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入樽, 落粗鹽(我用梅重量0既20%鹽), 樽頂用&quot;重石&quot;壓實, 我用左食物袋加水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jG1ApS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjG1ApS2.jpg&h=299e66f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一個月後, 出黎0既汁叫做&quot;梅酢&quot; 已經浸過晒D梅<br />\n一個月中間要周不時開蓋噴食用酒精消毒(噴落重石度)<br />\n好好彩成個月冇發霉 平平安安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sezm4U7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsezm4U7.jpg&h=538485be&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n搵一連4日都好天0既日子 READY拎去曬<br />\n每日反一反, 傍晚收返入屋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Kt7f2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Kt7f2W.jpg&h=6421f60c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第4日可以收成了 (梅表面白色粉係鹽結晶)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iv92PrG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiv92PrG.jpg&h=d0bb3f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入返乾淨0既樽, 雖然可即食但味道仲未變化<br />\n要等起碼3個月D鹽0既&quot;咸辣&quot;味先會消除<br />\n而家等10月中後就食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPS. 日本仲好常見落埋鮮紫蘇葉 咁D梅會變紫紅又好味<br />\n可惜香港搵唔到<br />\n所以呢隻係最基本0既白梅干"},{"pid":"2f6e87ed937a7f282607ac585c6032a04ed503c1","tid":2193138,"uid":340796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"鐘意浸酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033b3fb027342b0a62642cdfc230c1b4086fdc39","tid":2193138,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:57:05.000Z","msg":"幫推 好靚"},{"pid":"4f1d11317f60c4793e61ad8c594fd39d047de565","tid":2193138,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:57:33.000Z","msg":"梅干師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20170c8f0abfee9a26ea014bf6bdda2ac75d8101","tid":2193138,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f6e87ed937a7f282607ac585c6032a04ed503c1","tid":2193138,"uid":340796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"鐘意浸酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"一齊研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im